## âš™ï¸ Configuration Notes (Securityâ€‘First)

This repository **does not include any real secrets**.

To enable Google OAuth locally, configure the following via environment variables or a local development config file:

```json
"GoogleAuth": {
  "ClientId": "YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID",
  "ClientSecret": "YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET"
}
```

This follows industry best practices and prevents credential leakage.

